orders the field operators and multiplies by the sign of the\ntime order.\n\nThe notation `𝓣ᶠ(a)` is used for `timeOrderF a` ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/TimeOrder.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.«term𝓣ᶠ(_)»","kind":"def","line":45,"name":"FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.«term𝓣ᶠ(_)»","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L45-L46"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/TimeOrder.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.timeOrderF\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</span>.<span class=\"name\">timeOrderF</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</a></span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Module/LinearMap/Defs.html#LinearMap\">→ₗ[</a><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Module/LinearMap/Defs.html#LinearMap\">]</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For a field specification `𝓕`, `timeOrderF` is the linear map\n\n`FieldOpFreeAlgebra 𝓕 →ₗ[ℂ] FieldOpFreeAlgebra 𝓕`\n\ndefined by its action on the basis `ofCrAnListF φs`, taking\n`ofCrAnListF φs` to\n\n`crAnTimeOrderSign φs • ofCrAnListF (crAnTimeOrderList φs)`.\n\nThat is, `timeOrderF` time-orders the field operators and multiplies by the sign of the\ntime order.\n\nThe notation `𝓣ᶠ(a)` is used for `timeOrderF a` ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/TimeOrder.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.timeOrderF","kind":"def","line":28,"name":"FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.timeOrderF","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L28-L43"}}],"imports":["Init","PhysLean.QFT.PerturbationTheory.FieldSpecification.TimeOrder","PhysLean.QFT.PerturbationTheory.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.SuperCommute"],"instances":[],"name":"PhysLean.QFT.PerturbationTheory.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.TimeOrder"}